            </p>
            <div class="ratio ratio-16x9">
                <iframe
                    src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=9.963361,-84.047639&z=17&output=embed"
                    style="border:0;" allowfullscreen loading="lazy">
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <span class="eyebrow">Hablemos</span>
            <h2 class="mb-3 texto-acento">Contáctanos</h2>
            <ul class="list-unstyled fs-5">
                <li class="mb-3">
                    <strong>Teléfono:</strong>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/50685687154" target="_blank" class="font-mono">8568-7154 (WhatsApp)</a>
                </li>
                <li class="mb-3">
                    <strong>Correo:</strong>
                    <a href="mailto:bio-sport@hotmail.com">bio-sport@hotmail.com</a>
                </li>
                <li class="mb-3">
                    <strong>Facebook:</strong>
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/p/Gimnasio-Bio-Sport-100050566386030/?locale=es_LA" target="_blank">
                        Gimnasio Bio Sport
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="mb-3">
                    <strong>Instagram:</strong>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/gimnasiobiosportmoravia/" target="_blank">
                        @@gimnasiobiosportmoravia
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://wa.me/50685687154?text=Hola%2C%20me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20recibir%20informaci%C3%B3n" target="_blank" class="btn btn-success btn-lg mt-3">Únete a la Familia BioSport</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
